lead_paragraph: If it was not for a rain delay, Richard Gasquet said, he would not have made it to the last eight of his home grand slam for the first time in 13 attempts on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Rain Interruption Was Crucial, Says Gasquet
headline.main: Rain Interruption Was Crucial, Says Gasquet
